title: You Have to Cleanse the Rock
description: What's on your radar?, Jenny calls Dave out for something he recently purchased that she thinks is ridiculous, Lauren tells us she did talk to HR about the pictures she found on her co-workers computer, Worst Date Wednesday, a woman wants to know Tina's perspective on being an only child because she's debating having a second child, Think Fast, and more!
